                     <interp inst="t17880227-70-person733" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have had the silver in my possession ever since; I found two little bits of silver on his bedstead.</p>
               <p>(The silver was produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of it.</p>
